  Even students 

 Create a small form with title and body fields.  On submit, send a  
	POST request to the same API endpoint (/posts)  and display a success  
	message once data is submitted. 

Add and Remove List Items Dynamically 

Create an HTML page containing: 

A text input field 

An Add Item button 

A Remove Last Item button 

An unordered list (<ul>) 

Task: 

When the Add Item button is clicked 

Take the value from the input field. 

Create a new <li> element. 

Add it to the list. 

When the Remove Last Item button is clicked: 

Remove the last <li> element from the list 

 

