	"Data fetched successfully" 
	and use .then() and .catch() to handle it. 

2.Change Content and Style using DOM 

Create an HTML page with a paragraph and a button 

Task: 

When the button is clicked 

Change the text of the paragraph to "Welcome to JavaScript DOM Manipulation". 

Change the paragraph color to blue 

Increase the font size to 24px 